Date: Wed, 7 Jan 2026 17:16:09 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 33/36] riscv: dts: eswin: Add cpu&devices scaling for EIC7700
 SoC

Add the operating-points-v2 to support cpu and other devices scaling
on ESWIN EIC7700 SoC.

Signed-off-by: Min Lin <linmin@eswincomputing.com>

Upstream-Status: Pending [https://github.com/hehuaneswincomputing/linux-next/commit/4eae506c3597ccdc6c6c3a1ca62fe961ce00210e]
---
